From 9cc244f8c42f9bdd46f9581aa70509ec51bcb7fe Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: William Horvath <william@horvath.blog>
Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 17:02:41 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Revert "GPU: Refcount Vulkan allocations to fix transfer
 corruption on defrag (#15127)"

Doesn't solve TSan issues or texture corruption. Using the WIP patch over this for now.

This reverts commit b4b9a037b6b442fdc379aa3a9fea46e169330312.
